    public abstract class NumberBlock<V extends java.lang.Number>

    The generic Block to display a pre-defended number value Note that in its current form, the expected value is not in its primitive form. This needs to be worked on ... might need a overhaul to Block.ValueBlock as generics can not accept primitives
